   {
      "body" : "The proportion of economic:spam is lopsided the more we encourage or allow OP_RETURN to flourish. OP_RETURN does not make bitcoin valuable; OP_RETURN is not something nearly any full-node operator wants to bear nor did we agree to store OP_RETURN data that did not represent legitimate economic transaction-based activity. It is an error to encourage anyone to do this who can't discover how to do it themselves.",
